						h3.page_title_home About me
						img.profile(src='https://markoblogpics.s3.amazonaws.com/images/cv_pic.png', alt='Marko Oksanen')
						p.profile
								small
								| Hello! I am the co-founder of Tebla. We're developing new way to discover the restaurants
								| you love. Tebla is a curated platform leveraging the local knowledge of the best places in your city.
								| Our aim is to change your experience of dining out to be effortless, constant discovery with quality places you can trust.
								| Never be disappointed while eating out again.
						p.profile
								small
								| I am passionate about everything I do. I love how entrepreneurship empowers people to create value in the world and
								| solve problems worth solving. I did my Master's thesis about entrepreneurship education and I am still on a journey to
								| be fully educated myself.
