				h3.page_title Education
				.page_content
					h4.blue	MSc Tech - Aalto University
					span.year
						| 2004 - 2012
					ul#education
							li Degree completed with distinction at Aalto University 12.12.2012.
							li Majored in Knowledge Intensive Business (studied also: Leadership, IT, Strategy and Entrepreneurship).
