			#experience.page
				h3.page_title My experience
				.page_content
					h4.blue	Co-founder @ Tebla
					span.year
						| June 2014 -
					ul#education
							li We're building the next big thing.
					h4.blue	Product Manager @ Fyber
					span.year
						| July 2013 - June 2014
					ul#education
							li I started as owning a SponsorPay's strategic video product ("AppEngage"), and quickly evolved to being the product owner of the direct advertiser side of the business as well as holding the product owner role for the development team working on this side of the business.
					h4.blue	Researching entrepreneurship & Consulting
					span.year
						| March 2011 - July 2013
					ul#education
							li Co-founded the start-up Breakit. Leading the product development of a mobile application using agile development methodologies and developing back-end using modern JavaScript libraries. (June 2012 – )
							li Master's thesis about entrepreneurship and its education. My thesis was <a class="intext" href='http://tinyurl.com/mastersth'>published</a> by TEK (1000 copies).
							li Various consulting projects as an independent consultant through my company (Ideani). (March 2011 – )
					h4.blue	Analyst @ Accenture Oy
					span.year
						| June 2009 - July 2010
					ul#education
							li Specifying requirements together with customers and designing a quality ensurance process.
							li Independent software development project using Struts2 -framework.
					h4.blue	Product Manager / Software Engineer — Ironstar Helsinki Oy
					span.year
						| April 2007 - September 2008
					ul#education
							li Implemented agile methodologies (scrum).
							li Software development using object oriented design and technologies like J2EE, JSP, & SQL.
					br
